## Build & Dev Commands

<!--
  THE most-used section — the agent runs these dozens of times per session.
  Copy-paste correct, including container prefixes. Group by area. Include the
  one-time local setup at the end, not the beginning (it's needed once).
-->

```bash
{start the dev environment}
{build / watch}
{run unit tests}
{run lint / format check — and the auto-fix variant}
{run E2E tests — plus the recorded/headed variant if you have one}
{deploy — or point to the skill/runbook that owns deployment}
```

